description: Total number of Gauges found in all Instances
Grand total of all Gauge values on all Instances
Average of all Gauge values on all Instances
HTTP SD Number of discovered targets
Current number of Targets in Scrape Pool
Time to sync Scrape pool Quantile 0.5

query: (sum by(instance) (irate(node_cpu_seconds_total{job="node", mode!="idle"}[1m])) / on(instance) group_left sum by (instance)((irate(node_cpu_seconds_total{job="node"}[1m])))) * 100
(sum by(instance) (irate(node_cpu_seconds_total{job="node", mode!="idle"}[5m])) / on(instance) group_left sum by (instance)((irate(node_cpu_seconds_total{job="node"}[5m])))) * 100
